<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2013/08/07/spring-framework-3-2-4-released">Spring Framework 3.2.4 Released</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon releases"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/releases">Releases</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="https://gravatar.com/avatar/abbd9da647d544664816f5212717aba2?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<a class="author" href="/team/pwebb">Phil Webb</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2013-08-07 01:53:00.0">August 7, 2013</time>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="1137" href="/blog/2013/08/07/spring-framework-3-2-4-released#disqus_thread">
</a></div>
</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p></p>
<p>The fourth maintenance release in the Spring 3.2.x line is now available via <a href="https://search.maven.org/#search%7Cga%7C1%7Cg%3A%22org.springframework%22">Maven Central</a>, the <a href="https://github.com/SpringSource/spring-framework/wiki/Downloading-Spring-artifacts#wiki-resolving-spring-artifacts">SpringSource repository</a>, or for direct download from our <a target="_blank" href="http://www.springsource.com/download/community?project=Spring%20Framework&amp;version=3.2.4.RELEASE">community download page</a>. This release includes numerous <a href="https://jira.springsource.org/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10000&amp;version=14143">bugfixes and improvements</a> including an <a href="https://jira.springsource.org/browse/SPR-10806">important security fix</a> for Spring OXM. We recommend that all all users upgrade.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://www.springsource.com/download/community?project=Spring%20Framework&amp;version=3.2.4.RELEASE">Download</a> | <a href="http://static.springsource.org/spring/docs/3.2.4.RELEASE/spring-framework-reference/html/">Documentation</a> | <a target="_blank" href="http://static.springsource.org/spring/docs/3.2.4.RELEASE/javadoc-api/">Javadoc API</a> | <a target="_blank" href="http://static.springsource.org/spring/docs/3.2.4.RELEASE/changelog.txt">Change Log</a> | <a href="http://jira.springframework.org/browse/SPR">JIRA</a> </p>
</div>
</section>
<a class="blog-preview--readmore desktop-only" href="/blog/2013/08/07/spring-framework-3-2-4-released">
Read more...
</a>
</article>
